[[File:Kouka jinja2009-6.jpg|thumb|right|220px|Statue of "Takamitsu-kō and Sarutorahebi" at {{ill|Kōka Shrine (Seki)|ja|高賀神社|12=draft}}, {{ill|Seki, Gifu|ja|関市|12=draft}}]]
